snippet.title: AEW Fight Forever | SEASON PASS 4 Has Arrived!
snippet.description:
#AEW #AEWDynamite #aewcollision 

Season 4 of #AEWFightForever is here! This season features Samoa Joe, Adam Copeland and Jay White! Also included are 2 all-new arenas, 30 new moves, over 50 new custom attires, 10 music tracks, a Stadium Stampede Expansion and an all-new Tournament Mode.

Get the Season Pass 4 today on Xbox, PlayStation, Switch and PC for $19.99!

The golden era of wrestling games is back! AEW: Fight Forever is available now on your favorite console and PC!  Buy it now! - https://aew.thqnordic.com/

Watch AEW on TV
• AEW Dynamite airs every Wednesday night 8e/7c on TBS
• AEW Rampage airs every Friday night 10e/9c on TNT
• AEW Collision airs every Saturday at 8e/7c on TNT
